

This is the fast Installation notice :


    1)add code repository 

    3)chown and chmod the root server directory to the right user
    1) create all dirs :
        mkdir /var/www/logs 
        touch /var/www/logs/log.txt
        touch /var/www/logs/error.txt
        touch /var/www/logs/auth.txt
        touch /var/www/logs/command.txt
        mkdir /var/www/xml
        mkdir /var/www/zip
        mkdir /var/www/mp3
        mkdir /var/www/png
        mkdir /var/www/fichiers_finale
        mkdir /var/www/images_jpg
        mkdir /var/www/images_table_matieres
        mkdir /var/www/images_titres
        mkdir /var/www/incipits_jpg
        mkdir /var/www/js
        mkdir /var/www/jquery
        mkdir /var/www/css
        mkdir /var/www/include
        mkdir /var/www/images
        mkdir /var/www/images/design
    2)copy include/cfg_fields_default.xml in the root page to /var/www/include/cfg_fields.xml
        
        
